---
/**
 * Result cell — the evidence band. A full-width recessed `--well` strip
 * with hairline top/bottom rules holding one of the viz primitives; the
 * optional `header` slot carries the mono caption row above the chart so
 * the label and the picture read as one instrument.
 */
---

<div
  class="border-y border-black/10 bg-[color:var(--well)] px-6 py-7 md:px-10 md:py-8 dark:border-white/10"
>
  <slot name="header" />
  <slot />
</div>
